{"tid":1404151,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"將軍澳警署對面有商場","createTime":"2019-08-04T03:00:52.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-04T09:16:34.000Z","uid":288559,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"5d0b3ab10999eb3f2292d364d1c332bef8272404","tid":1404151,"uid":288559,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T03:00:52.000Z","msg":"如果你今日入將軍澳一定要來睇呢個post<span style=\"font-size: large;\"></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">因為新都城二期係公共交通運輸署行出去（即係新都城街市），對面就係狗署<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JxPsWx4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJxPsWx4.png&h=11d5f1c0&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6rpAkZM.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6rpAkZM.png&h=eef0de83&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/SJ799S7.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSJ799S7.png&h=973c813a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n要走嘅話<br />\n可以選擇搭電梯上返去新都城<br />\n然後行返去地鐵站度走<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">又或者：</span></span><br />\n沿住呢條路一直行出去<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7T6V5uq.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7T6V5uq.png&h=1000d53e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n最前面就係商場加戲院<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n轉左出邊就係地鐵站 仲有小學<br />\n<br />\n呢個post以防不時之需<br />\n覺得有需要就推<br />\nSorry for 1999<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0ffdbfbf5e054133f0ab35a386432f6d5329b6a8","tid":1404151,"uid":108337,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T03:02:39.000Z","msg":"好適合琴日既遠攻小隊<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pi